  "title": "‼️ENTRY LEVEL‼️TRAVEL✈️ TURN YAP INTO CASH💰 Events & Marketing Representative",
  "description": "<p>🚨 HEY YOU — DON’T SCROLL YET 🚨<br /><br />Got energy? Got confidence? Let’s put it to work‼️😎</p><p>No desk job. No boring routines. Just real interactions & real growth.<br /><br />We’re looking for a <strong>Events & Marketing Representative</strong> based in Simgapore to join our FUN and VIBRANT team that will support you in your journey here — <strong>Shaping you to be a better version of yourself.</strong></p><p><strong>🎤 What You’ll Be Doing</strong></p><p>• Represent exciting brands at pop-ups & events</p><p>• Chat, engage & create good vibes with people</p><p>• Build confidence, communication & people skills</p><p>• Work alongside a supportive, high-energy team 🎉</p><p><strong>💰 What You’ll Get</strong></p><p>• Personal growth + career exposure 🚀</p><p>• Travel opportunities ✈️</p><p>• Hands-on coaching from experienced mentors 💪</p><p><strong>👀 Who This Is For:</strong></p><p>• Outgoing, positive & willing to learn</p><p>• No experience needed — training provided</p><p>• Students, fresh grads & ORD welcome 🥳</p><p><strong>🫵🏻 Why Join Us?</strong></p><p>Because growth should be <strong>fun</strong>, not <em>boring</em>.</p><p>Real <u>skills</u>. Real <u>rewards</u>. Real <u>people</u>.</p><p>ARE YOU​ A THRIVER? <strong>Apply now</strong> & start building your confidence today! 🤩</p>",
